{"tid":1526314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗仔女用令牌收保護費] 每人要俾20蚊佢","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:47:25.000Z","uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62e358db1ad431ab0542ede3594080a0cfb8e900","tid":1526314,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190830/s00001/deea048de6ad36de37b614222779c178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190830%2Fs00001%2Fdeea048de6ad36de37b614222779c178.jpg&h=01cdad1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先喺街, 聽到應該係狗仔女講, 我有令牌. 明天返學全學校長, 老師, 學生都要聽佢話. <br />\n仲要叫全班每人每個月俾20蚊佢. <br />\n如果唔係話用令牌CALL警察. 話校長, 老師, 學生欺凌佢. <br />\n邊個唔聽話. 就叫警察捉佢返去打到佢殘廢. <br />\n仲好囂張咁話, 睇下D 警察打到人殘廢. 都冇事架. 我哋警察做乜都冇錯<br />\n喺學校, 邊個有令牌就大晒, 校長都要聽佢吩咐<br />\n<br />\n所以各位同學, 明天開學, 就係睇下身邊邊個同學有呢個&quot;令牌&quot;. 記得要做佢跟班. 佢去廁格都要跟埋佢入廁格呀! 準備麻包裝/垃圾袋. 以免馬桶塞咗冇得去<br />\n<br />\nPS: 喺街聽到目測11-12歲左右既o靚仔講"},{"pid":"b6e6ede0005b4867637b3222363f3e7af559499c","tid":1526314,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa65171ca458b3c53930f65a97257057a672679c","tid":1526314,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"已fc，朋友都fc左"},{"pid":"9d5b0ef68c5cd04067691b4d2f0a23202629e690","tid":1526314,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa65171ca458b3c53930f65a97257057a672679c","tid":1526314,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"已fc，朋友都fc左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"原來班特權人仕有晒相同諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}